I had considered on creating a guild database to compliment my inhabitant database.   However, it appears one has already been created (okay, so I slacked off with an EQ addiction for a time) at EQ Vault.  Instead of effort duplication, simply click here to be directed to this database.   It should be noted that they also have a player database which can link TO the guild database (nice feature, wish I'd have thought of that first).

For the record, my inhabitant database will remain for the moment, unless others feel there is no need to keep it around.  At that point you'd need to use the one at EQ Vault.  But, I kinda like having that database so it'll stay.
